== Procol Buffers ==
Protocol buffers are used to communicate data between the various Clacks
components.
Protobuf-C (A C implementation of Protocol Buffers)
  https://github.com/protobuf-c/protobuf-c
This library also requires an installation of the Protocol Buffers library.

== CMake ==
Any up to date version will do.

== libUUID ==
Should be provided by _most_ good *NIX / Linux distributions.

== Hiredis ==
Redis C client library.
  https://github.com/redis/hiredis
